data.description: This immaculate custom home with over 2,000 SqFt of living area sits on a beautifully landscaped 1 acre lot in the “sunbelt” of Hawaiian Paradise Park. Only a few blocks from the ocean, it exudes curb appeal!  The lush, well-thought-out, mature landscaping, with an abundance of tropical fruit trees, palms, flowers, and an expansive grassy yard, is your own personal botanical garden. The custom aluminum fence is perched on top of a lava rock wall that spans the front of the property. The concrete driveway leads to your enclosed two car garage with lots of extra room for secured storage. The acre is fully fenced, ideal for children and pets to safely enjoy the outdoors. A custom security screen door greets you at the formal front entrance.  The chef in your family will love the gorgeous kitchen that boasts plenty of hardwood cabinets, expansive white quartz countertops, modern Samsung appliances, and a casual dining bar with pendant lights that comfortably seats four. The formal dining area is complete with a butler’s pantry. The spacious living room has a glass sliding door that seamlessly connects you to the outdoors. The large covered back lanai has two ceiling fans, and is the perfect place for enjoying outdoor dining and entertaining. The master suite has a walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bath with two sinks, and custom tiled walk-in shower with two rainfall shower heads. There are two sizable guest bedrooms and a guest bath. The bonus room off of the living room is permitted as an office, but could be used as a 4th bedroom.   Vaulted ceilings, ample windows, ceiling fans, and vinyl floors throughout. Wall mounted A/C in the living room, master suite, and two guest bedrooms keep the home refreshingly cool. Indoor laundry room between the kitchen and the garage. Well water with UV filter and on demand hot water heater. Come see your slice of paradise! Shown by appt.  Take a virtual tour: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=5KVwRojFW1a
